org.xbis
Class DefaultQName

java.lang.Object
  org.xbis.DefaultQName
Direct Known Subclasses:
DefaultNameMap.LinkedQName
public class DefaultQName
extends java.lang.Object

XML Binary Information Set name information. This class is used for models which do not include support for unique element and attribute qnames. It holds the pair consisting of local name and namespace information, which together make up the unique name identification used by XMLS.

Version:
0.8
Author:
Dennis M. Sosnoski
